                "questionText": "Cho tam giác <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/12/58cc1776-48f2-4eb0-9727-8f47ff3cdf3c.png\"/> vuông tại <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/12/b5532ef6-07bf-496c-ac2b-464059e30c15.png\"/> đường cao <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/12/7be7b7fc-0bca-4ff1-a385-386688f40109.png\"/> Từ <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/12/0d2f949f-deea-4e3b-b448-17fed5377233.png\"/> kẻ <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/12/480af8e5-9c31-40f5-b457-26739669be49.png\"/> vuông góc với <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/12/fe5a4dc8-a110-4d8a-a431-06f2c765d10a.png\"/> vuông góc với <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/12/a7ce03b2-2eed-408b-aabc-c8fc26c7ba83.png\"/>\n<br>a) Chứng minh <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/12/c92b511e-6251-4d8f-84e8-01f18581f999.png\"/> là hình chữ nhật.\n<br>b) Gọi <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/12/52c57cfa-bf1c-4ecc-9622-e360dacc547a.png\"/> là trung điểm của <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/12/cabd096c-e2f2-4ef2-97e7-83f3d06c00c0.png\"/> Trên tia đối của tia <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/12/941a5cbe-796a-43b3-bf18-3813cca58c9d.png\"/> lấy điểm <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/12/2feef383-16ce-439d-b8d9-37c015107949.png\"/> sao cho <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/12/681f621e-6fa3-47d9-bc6c-8ba41525560b.png\"/> là trung cùa <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/12/345c149b-c23e-4866-beae-6e8f30be246a.png\"/> Chứng minh <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/12/2f786374-037c-40fd-9922-34f5dca70691.png\"/> là hình bình hành.\n<br>c) Chứng minh ba điểm <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/12/35936f4e-0677-48b1-8351-57c1907283a3.png\"/> thẳng hàng.\n",
                "answer": "<img src=\"https://asset.moon.vn/img/chat/large/2025/12/667bb62d-3e38-4486-9e36-0e26398414c8.jpg\" data-filename=\"\" style=\"max-width: 600px; height: auto;\"><br>a) Xét tứ giác <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/12/a76268f3-da94-4f83-ad72-541b702e5c26.png\"/> có: <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/12/64f6c6a6-9ec5-4fc2-a5a3-b4ea0260d8d2.png\"/> (do <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/12/32f323d6-d62e-4d0e-9f73-851f9ff6dc6b.png\"/> vuông tại <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/12/a2dbfda3-c636-460f-b366-d6fae9ca7497.png\"/>)\n<br><img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/12/2c0a0c3f-0d79-4f43-8400-7dcf6c53d127.png\"/>(do <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/12/9aaa9cd6-ace7-4926-9e32-4d38b6488a95.png\"/> tại <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/12/5330025a-c48d-405f-af36-91c871cc5659.png\"/>) \n<br><img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/12/204449d1-9096-4571-b4d6-777831bb3357.png\"/> (do <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/12/fb2c0185-174d-4d92-9592-d70ba9ad3fc1.png\"/> tại <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/12/f5db1942-16fb-412d-bfd5-8e0b392c77c9.png\"/>)\n<br>Suy ra tứ giác <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/12/0511f0ee-b198-4995-a55b-dcddbb31f556.png\"/> là hình chữ nhật (dhnb)\n<br>b) Tứ giác <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/12/c737e388-a0b8-4f68-9e03-d801a34b585b.png\"/> có 2 đường chéo <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/12/e7b3743c-a06b