tex/2025/12/bd7aef8a-aacc-4c95-9911-b736b513ac29.png\"/> hay <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/12/d53451af-3fd1-4641-9ae8-299a78e17a2b.png\"/>\n<br>Suy ra 3 điểm <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/12/63f7fc61-edf2-466a-a582-01453a82dfab.png\"/> thẳng hàng.\n",
